OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1779238996
OL,3,CBodies of two Italian divers recovered
OL,4,Cfrom an underwater cave in the Maldives
OL,6,FFinnish divers have recovered two more
OL,7,Fbodies after a group of Italians died
OL,8,Fon scuba diving trip in the Maldives.
OL,10,FAccording to officials, three divers
OL,11,Fretrieved the bodies, which were lying
OL,12,Fat a depth of around 60 metres -
OL,13,Fdouble the legal depth for
OL,14,Frecreational diving in the Maldives,
OL,15,Fwhich is 30 metres.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
