OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1779238996
OL,3,CBodies of two Italian divers recovered
OL,4,Cfrom an underwater cave in the Maldives
OL,6,FMohamed Hussain Shareef, the chief
OL,7,Fspokesperson for the Maldives'
OL,8,Fgovernment, told ITV News' US partner
OL,9,FCNN that the two bodies ` one male,
OL,10,Fone female ` were found deep inside a
OL,11,Fcave, and that they were being brought
OL,12,Fto the mortuary in Maldives' capital,
OL,13,FMale, by police.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
