PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1779238996
OL,3,CBodies of two Italian divers recovered
OL,4,Cfrom an underwater cave in the Maldives
OL,6,FThe body of diving instructor Gianluca
OL,7,FBenedetti was found outside of the
OL,8,Fcave last Thursday, the day the divers
OL,9,Fwere reported missing. Her body was
OL,10,Frecovered the same day.
OL,12,FThe other victims have been identified
OL,13,Fas Monica Montefalcone, an associate
OL,14,Fprofessor of ecology at the University
OL,15,Fof Genoa; her daughter, Giorgia
OL,16,FSommacal; marine biologist Federico
OL,17,FGualtieri; and researcher Muriel
OL,18,FOddenino, according to the Maldivian
OL,19,Fgovernment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
