OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1779238996
OL,3,CBodies of two Italian divers recovered
OL,4,Cfrom an underwater cave in the Maldives
OL,6,FTheir bodies were located inside the
OL,7,Fcave by the Finnish diving team on
OL,8,FMonday.
OL,10,FThe plan is to recover the remaining
OL,11,Ftwo bodies on Wednesday.
OL,13,FA multinational effort to locate and
OL,14,Fretrieve their remains was briefly
OL,15,Fpaused after a local military diver
OL,16,Fattempting to locate the bodies also
OL,17,Fdied. Authorities believe the death
OL,18,Fwas caused by decompression sickness.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
