PN,31505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1779238996
OL,3,CBodies of two Italian divers recovered
OL,4,Cfrom an underwater cave in the Maldives
OL,6,FWhen the search resumed on Monday,
OL,7,Fwith international support, the
OL,8,FFinnish divers found the bodies of the
OL,9,Ffour Italians in the deepest part of
OL,10,Fthe sea cave.
OL,12,FOn Monday, the Maldives government
OL,13,Fsaid that the bodies were spotted in
OL,14,Fthe innermost part of the cave by the
OL,15,Fthree Finnish diving experts,
OL,16,Fsupported by the Maldives police and
OL,17,Fthe military.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
