PN,31506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1779238996
OL,3,CBodies of two Italian divers recovered
OL,4,Cfrom an underwater cave in the Maldives
OL,6,FSpokesperson Ahmed Shaam said: "As was
OL,7,Fpreviously thought, the four bodies
OL,8,Fwere found inside the cave, not only
OL,9,Finside the cave, but well inside the
OL,10,Fcave into the third segment of the
OL,11,Fcave, which is the largest part."
OL,13,FHe said that the four bodies were
OL,14,Ffound "pretty much together."
