PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1779238996
OL,3,CBodies of two Italian divers recovered
OL,4,Cfrom an underwater cave in the Maldives
OL,6,FThe Divers' Alert Network Europe,
OL,7,Fwhich deployed the three Finnish
OL,8,Fdivers, said on its website that they
OL,9,Fare technical and cave divers with
OL,10,Finternational experience in search and
OL,11,Frecovery missions, including
OL,12,Foperations in "deep overhead
OL,13,Fenvironments, confined spaces and high-
OL,14,Frisk scenarios."
